      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know it might be a tear or something but its just like, a lot of hassle to go to the doctor and wait for hours. i've had sprains before and they usually just get better with ice and rest. how much ibuprofen should i take to deal with the swelling? like just a normal dose or should i take more to really knock it out? i really dont want to go to the hospital if i can just manage this at home.",
